  "text": "The defuzzification procedure considers the spread, height and shape of a triangular fuzzy number as important characteristics of the fuzzy number [CITATION_1] . The objective of defuzzification is to convert the output fuzzy variable to a crisp value. In other words, it is used to determine an exact value as the representative of the fuzzy number. To defuzzify the fuzzy weights in order to compare the alternatives in a non-fuzzy ranking method, the center of area (COA) is applied in this study using the following equation:",
